AB  - With the rapid development of modern information technology and the continuous advancement of school education reform, the development of school education management information has become the inevitable trend of education management reform and development in the information age. With the advent of the Internet of everything world, the new generation of information technology and entity are deeply integrated, as an important frontier of information technology 'digital twin technology' has become the focus. Digital twin technology refers to the use of information technologies such as the Internet of Things, big data, artificial intelligence and virtual reality to fully realize the digital expression of entities in the virtual world and form an information ecosystem of close-loop operation and intelligent decision-making with entities. In this paper, based on the actual development of colleges and universities, relying on the 'big data basis' and 'modeling ecosystem' of digital twin technology, combined with artificial intelligence algorithm, the digital twin technology is innovatively applied in the informatization of college education management. On the basis of multi-dimensional and multi-modal data collection and mining of college education management, a set of digital twin model of university education management informatization is constructed, and the model is applied in scene. By creating the digital twin education management system, we can realize the new mode of intelligent visual education management and promote the development of education management informatization. © 2024 IEEE.
