TI  - Integration of BIM Methodology and AR Technologies for Piping Learning in Buildings
PY  - 2024
T2  - Lecture Notes in Mechanical Engineering
SP  - 270
EP  - 279
DO  - 10.1007/978-3-031-51623-8_26
