AB  - The Metaverse Immersive Legal Gaming Experience System based on Gaussian Splatter Technology is an immersive interactive tool integrating metaverse technology with legal practice. It achieves high-precision rendering of virtual scenes through Gaussian splatter technology, combining virtual reality and digital twin technologies to enable digital role-playing, virtual courtroom recreation, and simulated trial processes. The system employs a massively multiplayer online (MMO) mode to train interactive models, generating immersive legal practice scenarios and aiding legal knowledge dissemination. It explores optimal application pathways in rule-of-law education practice, continuously enhancing system immersion and functional adaptability through optimized model development. © 2025 IEEE.
