AB  - With the expansion of the commercial space market scale and the development of low-orbit small satellite constellation applications, it is required that the satellite development cycle be shortened, the cost be reduced, and batch production be carried out. In this paper, the traditional satellite development process is analyzed firstly. Then, on the basis of the advantages and disadvantages of traditional satellite development process, a framework for the whole process of satellite intelligent development is designed, combining artificial intelligence technologies such as deep learning, digital twin technology and natural language processing technology. Finally, the technical challenges in intelligent development are analyzed to provide reference for the subsequent application of artificial intelligence technology in the field of satellite intelligent development. © 2025 SPIE.
