AB  - The appearance of Industry 4.0 and the expanding complexity of global supply chains require a paradigm move in manufacturing framework. This chapter presents the concept of an Ultra Smart Cyberspace Manufacturing Infrastructure (USCMI), a highly coordinates and intelligent ecosystem outlined to revolutionize modern generation. The USCMI leverages cutting-edge innovations counting Artificial Intelligence (AI), Machine Learning (ML), Industrial Internet of Things (IIoT), digital twins, and progressed mechanical autonomy, all coordinated through a sophisticated Automated Smart Engineering (ASE) system. This unique outlines the key structural components, innovative enablers, and expected benefits of USCMI, highlighting its potential to enhance efficiency, reduce waste, improve quality, cultivate advancement, and construct unprecedented strength within the confront of disturbances, ultimately clearing the way for truly lights-out and universally distributed manufacturing operations. © 2026, IGI Global Scientific Publishing. All rights reserved.
