TI  - AI-Powered Mixed Reality for Reviving Al-Khwarizmi’s Heritage in Inclusive Education: A Digital Twin Approach
PY  - 2026
T2  - Lecture Notes in Computer Science
VL  - 15741 LNCS
SP  - 547
EP  - 558
DO  - 10.1007/978-3-031-97775-6_34
