PY  - 2025
T2  - Proceedings of the 4th 2025 International Conference on Smart Cities, Automation and Intelligent Computing Systems, ICON-SONICS 2025
SP  - 101
EP  - 108
DO  - 10.1109/ICON-SONICS67145.2025.11309261
