AB  - The rapid development of information technology, computer technology, and communication technology has not only changed the way people live and work, but also has a huge impact on the way of learning and the development of education. The rapid development of the Internet has promoted online learning to become one of the main forms of people's learning; the development of cloud computing and 5G technology has promoted the convenience and equalization of the acquisition of educational resources; the application of virtual reality and augmented reality technology has solved the security issue in education scenarios Technology is no longer used in education in a single form. The integration of intelligent technologies such as 'big data + AI' has become a new driving force and way of thinking in the current society. After all, intelligent technology will exist in all aspects of educational activities like multimedia technology, and how it is applied to educational scenarios, how to influence and change education are topics that need to be continuously explored. Through case analysis, the article attempts to explore the ways and methods of intelligent technology and its core algorithm applied in education and teaching activities, as well as the impact of intelligent technology on education and teaching activities.  © 2021 IEEE.
