AB  - Science and technology has promoted the deep integration of information technology and education teaching mode. Flipped classroom, MOOC and micro class teaching modes have been far from meeting the needs of science and technology innovation in China, which is in urgent need of innovative talents. Therefore, the reform of education and teaching mode in Colleges and universities is imminent. This research is based on the digital twin technology, which brings new opportunities for professional education in Colleges and universities. Through the micro smart factory of Beihua University in Jilin Province, the digital twin technology is used to construct the online open course teaching digital platform of innovation engineering practice, and the application ideas of mechanical automation professional education based on digital twin technology are proposed, It also provides new ideas and ideas for the development of related courses in other colleges and universities.  © 2021 ACM.
