AB  - According to the orientation of vocational-oriented higher education and the requirements of Shanghai Municipal Education Commission for first-class undergraduate training of practical talents, the main direction of laboratory construction in universities tends to be “integration of production and education”. In particular, the experimental training platform constructed should meet the production process and production equipment status of actual manufacturing enterprises. Therefore, after three-year construction, the laboratory of Shanghai Polytechnic University Intelligent Manufacturing Factory is characterized by digital twin technology and virtual simulation technology of intelligent manufacturing, with the goal of integrating production and education. It is planned to build the laboratory into an a intelligent manufacturing demonstration center with integrated teaching and scientific research, reasonable system, open, sharing and distinctive features. © 2021, The Author(s), under exclusive license to Springer Nature Singapore Pte Ltd.
