AB  - To make up for the shortcomings of low efficiency, high risk and weak pertinence in traditional engineering training, an engineering training model based on digital twin technology is proposed. In the process of constructing this model, the connotation of digital twin under the background of engineering training is explained, and the construction method of digital twin is presented. At the same time, the construction method of the training platform is put forward, including the overall architecture design of training software, system communication architecture design, platform resource construction and resource management scheme design. Finally, by taking electrical power system training as an example, the specific implementation process of this model is described, which shows the feasibility of the application of the industrial training model based on digital twin. © 2022 Tsinghua University Press. All rights reserved.
