AB  - With the advent of the Internet era, the cost of realizing virtual characters has been greatly reduced. The high cost and low efficiency exhibited by traditional virtual technology can't meet social needs. People are seeking fast, convenient and accurate virtual character reproduction technology. Through researching the characteristics of the characters appearance, language habits, voice tone and so on, the research direction of this paper is to simulate and reshape voice and images, construct a cloud platform-based on user-side and client-side, and integrate deep learning, natural language processing, digital twins and other technologies to an immersive 4D intelligent interactive platform. The platform under in the form of application software provides integrated services of intelligent voice interaction and virtual character interaction. In the industrial diagnosis mode, the transition from traditional video retention and voice retention to a new intelligent voice recognition and simulation mode is realized.  © 2021 IEEE.
